{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:32:06.081Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call_output","id":"ctco_019f7b6f-6641-7531-8db6-178c0d46e9a5","call_id":"call_NrZ9WeTj75Y90VNpVtRBGPDi","output":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Script completed\nWall time 5.0 seconds\nOutput:\n"},{"type":"input_text","text":"{\"chunk_id\":\"52bfc2\",\"wall_time_seconds\":5.001428292,\"session_id\":21313,\"original_token_count\":856,\"output\":\"\\u001b[0;0H\\u001b[JRefreshing run status every 10 seconds. Press Ctrl+C to quit.\\r\\n\\r\\n* main E2E Baseline · 29696736813\\r\\nTriggered via push about 8 minutes ago\\r\\n\\r\\nJOBS\\r\\n✓ Require protected main E2E source in 2s (ID 88218679538)\\r\\n  ✓ Set up job\\r\\n  ✓ Reject unprotected E2E refs\\r\\n  ✓ Complete job\\r\\nX Playwright E2E (functional + docs) in 7m50s (ID 88218687174)\\r\\n  ✓ Set up job\\r\\n  ✓ Validate required configuration\\r\\n  ✓ Checkout repository\\r\\n  ✓ Setup Bun\\r\\n  ✓ Setup Node\\r\\n  ✓ Install dependencies\\r\\n  ✓ Install Playwright browsers\\r\\n  ✓ Pull Docker images (compose)\\r\\n  ✓ Build Docker images (compose)\\r\\n  ✓ Start Docker stack for E2E\\r\\n  ✓ Start application and polling worker containers\\r\\n  ✓ Wait for application\\r\\n  X Run Playwright suites\\r\\n  ✓ Collect Docker logs\\r\\n  ✓ Stop Docker stack\\r\\n  ✓ Upload Playwright test results\\r\\n  ✓ Upload generated docs\\r\\n  - Post Setup Node\\r\\n  - Post Setup Bun\\r\\n  ✓ Post Checkout repository\\r\\n  ✓ Complete job\\r\\n\\r\\nANNOTATIONS\\r\\n! Node.js 20 is deprecated. The following actions target Node.js 20 but are being forced to run on Node.js 24: actions/checkout@34e114876b0b11c390a56381ad16ebd13914f8d5, actions/setup-node@49933ea5288caeca8642d1e84afbd3f7d6820020, actions/upload-artifact@ea165f8d65b6e75b540449e92b4886f43607fa02. For more information see: https://github.blog/changelog/2025-09-19-deprecation-of-node-20-on-github-actions-runners/\\r\\nPlaywright E2E (functional + docs): .github#2\\r\\n\\r\\nX Process completed with exit code 1.\\r\\nPlaywright E2E (functional + docs): .github#4401\\r\\n\\r\\n-   1 failed\\r\\n    [local-chrome-baseline] › tests/specs/profile/user-profile-edit.spec.ts:18:5 › profile edit persists notification email and reimbursement details \\r\\n  51 did not run\\r\\n  98 passed (3.6m)\\r\\nPlaywright E2E (functional + docs): .github#4363\\r\\n\\r\\nX   1) [local-chrome-baseline] › tests/specs/profile/user-profile-edit.spec.ts:18:5 › profile edit persists notification email and reimbursement details \\r\\n    Error: expect(locator).toHaveValue(expected) failed\\r\\n\\r\\n    Locator:  getByRole('dialog', { name: 'Edit profile' }).getByRole('textbox', { name: 'PayPal email (for reimbursements)', exact: true })\\r\\n    Expected: \\\" profile-paypal-1789430400000@evorto.app \\\"\\r\\n    Received: \\\"\\\"\\r\\n    Timeout:  5000ms\\r\\n\\r\\n    Call log:\\r\\n      - Expect \\\"toHaveValue\\\" with timeout 5000ms\\r\\n      - waiting for getByRole('dialog', { name: 'Edit profile' }).getByRole('textbox', { name: 'PayPal email (for reimbursements)', exact: true })\\r\\n        14 × locator resolved to <input matinput=\\\"\\\" id=\\\"mat-input-4\\\" aria-invalid=\\\"false\\\" aria-required=\\\"false\\\" name=\\\"ng.form1.paypalEmail\\\" aria-describedby=\\\"mat-mdc-hint-6\\\" class=\\\"mat-mdc-input-element mat-mdc-form-field-input-control mdc-text-field__input cdk-text-field-autofill-monitored\\\"/>\\r\\n           - unexpected value \\\"\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n      13 |   await expect(field).not.toHaveClass(/mat-input-server/);\\r\\n      14 |   await field.fill(value);\\r\\n    > 15 |   await expect(field).toHaveValue(value);\\r\\n         |                       ^\\r\\n      16 | };\\r\\n      17 |\\r\\n      18 | test('profile edit persists notification email and reimbursement details', async ({\\r\\n        at fillControlledTextField (/home/runner/work/app/app/tests/specs/profile/user-profile-edit.spec.ts:15:23)\\r\\n        at /h