{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:32:19.399Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The post-merge gate caught a second CI-only race, this time before docs ran: the profile-edit test filled the PayPal field while the dialog’s asynchronous profile initialization was still able to reset it, so the value became empty. The merge itself is complete, but staging is correctly blocked. I’m treating this as another deterministic stabilization rather than rerunning and hoping.\n\nI’m using the Angular testing guidance now because this failure sits at the form/hydration boundary; it will guide the smallest durable wait and its verification.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:32:19.399Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","id":"msg_07acb54591783f13016a5d0a21bb588191a652c50cbcefafdc","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"The post-merge gate caught a second CI-only race, this time before docs ran: the profile-edit test filled the PayPal field while the dialog’s asynchronous profile initialization was still able to reset it, so the value became empty. The merge itself is complete, but staging is correctly blocked. I’m treating this as another deterministic stabilization rather than rerunning and hoping.\n\nI’m using the Angular testing guidance now because this failure sits at the form/hydration boundary; it will guide the smallest durable wait and its verification."}],"phase":"commentary","internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f7b3b-61db-7f22-b04f-a7cc62c9b8f9"}}}
