{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:48:09.157Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","id":"fco_019f7b7e-1845-7871-981d-7d0b8caf1584","call_id":"call_5U8iU3dxALBUSKtZhehq91f7","output":[{"type":"input_text","text":"Script completed\nWall time 10.1 seconds\nOutput:\n"},{"type":"input_text","text":"{\"chunk_id\":\"98b06e\",\"wall_time_seconds\":21.698475,\"exit_code\":1,\"original_token_count\":1616,\"output\":\"T°°°°°\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m\\u001b[0m\\u001b[31merror\\u001b[0m\\u001b[2m:\\u001b[0m script \\u001b[1m\\\"docker:webserver\\\"\\u001b[0m was terminated by signal SIGTERM \\u001b[2m(Polite quit request)\\u001b[0m\\u001b[0m\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mhelpers/testing/docker-webserver.sh: line 124: 18886 Terminated: 15          bun \\\"${wall_clock_timeout_script}\\\" 0 \\\"${timeout_termination_grace_seconds}\\\" docker compose \\\"$@\\\"\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Compose Stopping Aborting on container exit...\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-mailpit-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-worker-1 Error Error while Stopping\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-evorto-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-init-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-setup-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-stripe-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-init-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-init-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-setup-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-setup-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-init-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mminio-1       | INFO: Exiting on signal: TERMINATED\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-setup-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-1 Stopping \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.476 UTC [1] LOG:  received fast shutdown request\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.476 UTC [1] LOG:  aborting any active transactions\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.477 UTC [1] LOG:  background worker \\\"logical replication launcher\\\" (PID 32) exited with exit code 1\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.479 UTC [27] LOG:  shutting down\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.480 UTC [27] LOG:  checkpoint starting: shutdown immediate\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.527 UTC [27] LOG:  checkpoint complete: wrote 709 buffers (4.3%); 0 WAL file(s) added, 0 removed, 0 recycled; write=0.004 s, sync=0.037 s, total=0.049 s; sync files=984, longest=0.005 s, average=0.001 s; distance=10135 kB, estimate=10135 kB; lsn=0/3ED49A8, redo lsn=0/3ED49A8\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mdb-1          | 2026-07-19 17:48:08.530 UTC [1] LOG:  database system is shut down\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-stripe-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-stripe-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-stripe-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-minio-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-db-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-mailpit-1 Stopped \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-mailpit-1 Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22mError response from daemon: No such container: 7e65f568048eb0dc2990ef64d341dc33a6fb41200f1ef97e9bf83a79db029be3\\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Container evorto-f907c8db-mailpit-1 Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_mailpit-data Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_postgres-data Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_stripe-webhook Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Network evorto-f907c8db_default Removing \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_mailpit-data Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_stripe-webhook Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Volume evorto-f907c8db_postgres-data Removed \\n\\u001b[2m[WebServer] \\u001b[22m Network evorto-f907c8db_default Removed \\n\\n\\nComplete Playwright run required; incomplete tests found:\\n- /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44 >  > setup > setup/authentication.setup.ts > authenticate admin@evorto.app (skipped)\\n- /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44 >  > setup > setup/authentication.setup.ts > authenticate global-admin@evorto.app (skipped)\\n- /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44 >  > setup > setup/authentication.setup.ts > authenticate user@evorto.app (skipped)\\n- /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44 >  > setup > setup/authentication.setup.ts > authenticate organizer@evorto.app (skipped)\\n- /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44 >  > setup > setup/authentication.setup.ts > authenticate testuser2@evorto.app (skipped)\\n\\n  1) [setup] › tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44:8 › authenticate testuser1@evorto.app ────────\\n\\n    Test timeout of 60000ms exceeded.\\n\\n    Error: locator.fill: Test timeout of 60000ms exceeded.\\n    Call log:\\n      - waiting for locator('input[name=\\\"username\\\"], input[type=\\\"email\\\"]')\\n\\n\\n      60 |     await page\\n      61 |       .locator('input[name=\\\"username\\\"], input[type=\\\"email\\\"]')\\n    > 62 |       .fill(userData.email);\\n         |        ^\\n      63 |     await fillProtectedValue(\\n      64 |       page.locator('input[name=\\\"password\\\"], input[type=\\\"password\\\"]'),\\n      65 |       userData.passwordVariable,\\n        at /Users/hedde/.codex/worktrees/b7e9/evorto/tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:62:8\\n\\n  1 failed\\n    [setup] › tests/setup/authentication.setup.ts:44:8 › authenticate testuser1@evorto.app ─────────\\n  148 did not run\\n  1 passed (2.1m)\\nerror: script \\\"test:e2e\\\" exited with code 1\\n\"}"}],"internal_chat_message_metadata_passthrough":{"turn_id":"019f7b3b-61db-7f22-b04f-a7cc62c9b8f9"}}}
