{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:48:16.104Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The application tests themselves have not failed. The clean baseline is blocked before them by Auth0: the first login never renders a username field, then fail-fast correctly marks all remaining tests incomplete. I’m checking the generated worktree port against the callback URLs now; this matches the local-port constraint we discussed earlier, not the profile fix.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
