{"timestamp":"2026-07-19T17:52:29.491Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"web_search_end","call_id":"exec-80f65389-3d41-40ea-bcbf-3c2c8d27132a","query":"site:github.com/vercel-labs/portless README portless local development wildcard domains Auth0","action":{"type":"search","query":"site:github.com/vercel-labs/portless README portless local development wildcard domains Auth0"},"results":[{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search0","snippet":"vercel-labs / portless Public ... Replace port numbers with stable, named .localhost URLs for local development. ... portless proxy start --wildcard # Allow unregistered subdomains","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/portless: Replace port numbers with stable, named local URLs. For humans and agents. · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/portless"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search1","snippet":"We've verified that the organization vercel-labs controls the domain: ... 5. portless portless PublicReplace port numbers with stable, named local URLs. ... Captures your web","title":"Vercel Labs · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search2","snippet":"vercel-labs / open-agents Public ... Authentication is handled by Better Auth with Vercel and GitHub as social providers. ... For local development, use `http://localhost:3000` as","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/open-agents: An open source template for building cloud agents. · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/open-agents"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search3","snippet":"vercel env pull .env.local --environment=production ... # VERCEL_ENV=development # flips the Vercel-deployment gate so Redis connects ... # unset VERCEL_AUTH_MODE # use admin-secret auth locally","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/vercel-openclaw: Deploy OpenClaw on Vercel · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/vercel-openclaw"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search4","snippet":"## Development ... * portless — `npm i -g portless` ... All dev servers use portless to avoid hardcoded ports. ... Readme","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/wterm: A terminal emulator for the web · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/wterm"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search5","snippet":"git clone https://github.com/vercel-labs/coding-agent-template.git ... * `POSTGRES_URL`: Your PostgreSQL connection string (automatically provided when deploying to Vercel via the Neon integration, or","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/coding-agent-template: Multi-agent AI coding platform powered by Vercel Sandbox and AI Gateway · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/coding-agent-template"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search6","snippet":"The middleware (`middleware.ts`) intelligently detects subdomains across various environments (local development, production, and Vercel preview deployments). ... Push your repository to GitHub ... Se","title":"GitHub - vercel/platforms: A full-stack Next.js app with multi-tenancy. · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel/platforms"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search7","snippet":"Zig calls C directly, which keeps platform SDKs, native libraries, codecs, and local system integrations within reach when the WebView layer needs to do real","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/zero-native: Build native desktop + mobile apps with web UI and Zig · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/zero-native"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search8","snippet":"Perhaps you are looking for the \"preview deployment suffix\" add-on, which replaces \"vercel.app\" with an arbitrary domain for development purposes? ... I think this issue","title":"Wildcard subdomains in preview URLs? · vercel community · Discussion #475 · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel/community/discussions/475"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search9","snippet":"git clone https://github.com/vercel-labs/knowledge-agent-template.git ... # AI (optional — only needed for local dev, Vercel uses OIDC automatically)","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/knowledge-agent-template: Open source file-system and knowledge based agent template. Build AI agents that stay up to date with your knowledge base · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/knowledge-agent-template"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search10","snippet":"AI Gateway auth uses Vercel OIDC automatically on deployed Vercel environments — no extra configuration needed. ... Falls back to `openclaw-single` in local/non-Vercel environments. ...","title":"vercel-openclaw/docs/environment-variables.md at main · vercel-labs/vercel-openclaw · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/vercel-openclaw/blob/main/docs/environment-variables.md"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.com","ref_id":"turn269search11","snippet":"\"https://api.github.com/repos/myorg/\", ... url: \"https://ai-gateway.vercel.sh\", ... * Origin matching: URLs must match the exact origin (scheme + host + port)","title":"GitHub - vercel-labs/just-bash: Bash for Agents · GitHub","url":"https://github.com/vercel-labs/just-bash"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"education.github.com","ref_id":"turn269search12","snippet":"Retrieving updates from another repository and updating local repos ... matches or wildcard globs. ... GitHub is free for students and teach-","title":"git-cheat-sheet-education","url":"https://education.github.com/git-cheat-sheet-education.pdf?file=git-cheat-sheet-education.pdf"},{"type":"text_result","domain":"github.github.com","ref_id":"turn269search13","snippet":"GitHub Actions give you the flexibility to build automated software development lifecycle workflows. ... echo \"A little less ${message}\"","title":"Actions Cheat Sheet","url":"https://githu